      <div class="card">
        <h2>Fitness & Activity — No Gym Needed</h2>
        <p class="muted">Short routines you can do at home or during school breaks.</p>

        <h3>Beginner 10-minute bodyweight circuit</h3>
        <ol class="muted small">
          <li>30s Jumping jacks</li>
          <li>10 Air squats</li>
          <li>10 Push-ups (knees OK)</li>
          <li>20s Plank</li>
          <li>20s Walk or march in place</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="muted small">Repeat 2x if you can. Increase reps by 2–5 every week.</p>

        <h3>How to start</h3>
        <ul class="muted small">
          <li>Pick 3 days/week to do the circuit</li>
          <li>Track progress in a simple notebook or phone note</li>
          <li>Find a friend to do it with — accountability helps</li>
        </ul>
